summary: Creating Spotify Playlists for Swifties I’m inspired by the innovative ways we swifties connect globally online and since...
body:
Creating Spotify Playlists for Swifties

I’m inspired by the innovative ways we swifties connect globally online and since hitting 7.5k followers, I decided to try something new; Spotify. Taylor initially encouraged me by gifting us with musical playlists ~ so I’ve created multiple playlists in true swiftie theme; titles, tours, albums and now users. So far I’ve created playlists for four of my favourite swiftie Tumblr accounts;

@magic-madness-heaven titled ‘magic madness heaven sin’

@seleniftie titled ‘castle crumbled overnight’

@tayswiftnation titled ‘heartbreak is the national anthem’

@tropicoroses titled ‘isn’t it delicate?’

If you’d like a Spotify playlist created for you please comment below, note it may take a while since I want to give you the best possible jamming session. Each playlist made is produced specifically for that person from the name to the songs included, based from the account. Find these playlists under my Spotify username @georgia.clare.
